{"tid":2330297,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太極拳獲列為聯合國非物質文化遺產","createTime":"2020-12-18T01:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T04:58:35.000Z","uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"25ff1054d31c4a352a82804c1a0ecaceb6ed38f7","tid":2330297,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"太極拳獲聯合國教科文組織通過，列入人類非物質文化遺產代表作名錄。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國教科文組織保護非物質文化遺產委員會，召開網上會議，評審57個國家或地區申報的50個非物質文化遺產項目，中國單獨申報的太極拳經審議獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n太極拳自17世紀中葉形成以來，世代傳承，習練者遍布全國各地，並在海外有廣泛傳播和傳承。太極拳對於習練者的性別、年齡、體質、職業、民族並無限制，透過練習太極拳，民眾在修身養性、強身健體的同時，亦傳承著中華民族的文化基因。"},{"pid":"9ed1ccb0bf158491183a9a23536980dd23db24ac","tid":2330297,"uid":258345,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"緊係非物質啦<br />\n都打唔到人"},{"pid":"abfd1d23fb869941d68e4999610fe203672754ab","tid":2330297,"uid":106408,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"發神經<br />\n騙術都做到非物質文化遺產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b68a4166aba4123dca22c5c7b2db6725516b5ed","tid":2330297,"uid":63187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed1ccb0bf158491183a9a23536980dd23db24ac","tid":2330297,"uid":258345,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"緊係非物質啦<br />\n都打唔到人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b933b2342551ee799e159d5266001afcdb43d5b","tid":2330297,"uid":179409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:42:12.000Z","msg":"練到好多人膝頭有事唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打又唔打得<br />\n養身功效亦遠遠唔夠瑜伽嚟<br />\n純粹靠武俠神話吹出嚟嘅一個集體騙局"},{"pid":"cf1c0eb36a4f39aaddd575ec191411cefddb85e6","tid":2330297,"uid":25367,"like":0,"